name: Unofficial Microsoft Fluent 3D Emoji
description:
Add Microsoft fluent 3d emojis seamlessly onto your designs.


Simply select or search the emoji you want and Fluent 3D Emoji will add the png of the selected emoji.


3D emoji data are taken from (https://github.com/JustJordanT/Windows_11_Emjois).


If you have any issues or suggetions, hit me up on twitter
